<bibRefCitation author="Forster, R. R. &amp; Platnick, N. I. &amp; Gray, M. R." box="[873,1083,258,285]" pageId="3" pageNumber="526" pagination="1 - 116" refId="ref8525" refString="Forster, R. R., Platnick, N. I. &amp; Gray, M. R. (1987) A review of the spider superfamilies Hypochiloidea and Austrochiloidea (Araneae, Araneomorphae). Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History, 185, 1 - 116." type="journal article" year="1987">
Forster 
<emphasis box="[961,1010,258,284]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="526">et al</emphasis>
. 1987
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Lin, Y. J. &amp; Li, S. Q." box="[1094,1262,258,284]" pageId="3" pageNumber="526" pagination="17 - 29" refId="ref8775" refString="Lin, Y. J. &amp; Li, S. Q. (2020) Taxonomic studies on the genus Ectatosticta (Araneae, Hypochilidae) from China, with descriptions of two new species. ZooKeys, 954, 17 - 29. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 954.52254" type="journal article" year="2020">Lin &amp; Li 2020</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
